root: ^I don't think I want to perform again.
^I know. And I do love it, I really do! But now I'm not sure I'll be able to separate my performance from death.
^But don't worry. I'm not making any life-changing decisions just yet.
^I need some space to think before I do.
^That's a good idea. Just don't let something sad get in the way of doing what you want to do.
